A robotics startup captures attention by flying a small drone above its booth. Nearby, the engineering society sponsors a resume review table close to the stage, and students utilize tablets at kiosks to upload their resumes to the fair database. In a more relaxed area, friends decompress on the quad, discussing their experiences and sharing which companies responded positively to their outreach. Additionally, a data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance, and concurrently, an alumni panel discusses preparing for technical interviews. Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths, highlighting the variety of opportunities available at the fair. Workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom, and near the exit, a post-event survey link flashes on the monitors.
